<h1>Textbox</h1>

<p class="lead">Supercharge the humble textbox with more styling and data processing options.</p>

<h2>Simple textbox</h2>

<p>Use <code>f-textbox</code> to create a <a href="/api/havok/form/Textbox.html">havok/form/Textbox</a> to collect simple text data.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <d-formspy class="form-horizontal">
        <f-textbox value="hello"></f-textbox>
    </d-formspy>
</div>

